# STEP 2: ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á ultralytics ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏£‡∏ô YOLOv8 Classification
